# mcp-gateway: line-ending normalisation.
#
# Go and TypeScript sources must use LF on disk so a Windows runner
# with core.autocrlf=true cannot inject CRLF that confuses gofmt /
# byte-identical staleness checks (T-F.5 cross-Wave CI fix —
# tools/grammar-gen/internal/gen/gen_test.go::TestRender_RealGrammar_Smokes).
*.go        text eol=lf
*.ts        text eol=lf
*.tmpl      text eol=lf
*.yaml      text eol=lf
*.yml       text eol=lf
*.json      text eol=lf
*.md        text eol=lf
*.sh        text eol=lf
Makefile    text eol=lf

# Binary artefacts must not be CRLF-converted under any circumstance.
*.vsix      binary
*.png       binary
*.jpg       binary
*.gif       binary
